root: ^I know it must be ze biggest shock…let me put it back on.
^Shock?! Shock doesn’t even come close, you’re my brother!!
^You took advantage of me, you pig!
^No it wasn’t like that Helvezia! I was drunk as, how you say, skunk!
^Once the court is done with yo-
^It is all about ze money with you!
^You will never be happy zis way!
^How do I know you didn’t get pregnant for ze money?!
^Oh I don’t need to prostitute myself out to <b>you</> for money!
^There are men way better than you falling over themselves to give me money.
^You are ze meanest woman! Zis is why mother liked me better!
^Yes you just want to ride ze alimony pony.
^Oh I’ll ride it all the way to the bank!
